  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alice wandered into a land full of plants like nothing she'd ever seen before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the story of Alice and friends' adventure in a pixel-art world that's just like a storybook, told with adorable animations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/8241a13ec6b6a7d6fd96e3210249c7af.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/8241a13ec6b6a7d6fd96e3210249c7af.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/8241a13ec6b6a7d6fd96e3210249c7af.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance through the map with Alice, and aim to reach various endings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/a92288ff28998f7e78681518ea275bdd.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/a92288ff28998f7e78681518ea275bdd.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/a92288ff28998f7e78681518ea275bdd.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Slay the Alice is a short visual-novel adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All you'll need to use is a mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Within a single map, you'll choose which path to take, read randomly-occurring stories, and choose Alice's actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no difficult action elements, battles, or deduction elements involved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■How to Play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make choices, gather flowers, and reach the end of the map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/44e1274a86731f852d63cb81ac84c048.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/44e1274a86731f852d63cb81ac84c048.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/44e1274a86731f852d63cb81ac84c048.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・A short experience with around 30 minutes of playtime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Simple mouse-only controls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・No action gameplay, battles, or deduction elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Contains a few horror elements and graphic depictions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Four endings (and one bonus ending)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Multiple Endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alice's actions will slightly affect what ending you get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once all other endings are obtained, it will unlock an bonus ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/66f7814c8220d0857a4f84dded22be63.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/66f7814c8220d0857a4f84dded22be63.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/66f7814c8220d0857a4f84dded22be63.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Game Streaming and Creative Guidelines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We welcome game streaming, live broadcasts, and fan creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > For game streaming, live broadcasts,  be sure to paste the URL for \"Slay the Alice\" on Steam in the summary field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Monetization is also allowed without any issues.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alice wandered into a land full of plants like nothing she'd ever seen before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the story of Alice and friends' adventure in a pixel-art world that's just like a storybook, told with adorable animations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/8241a13ec6b6a7d6fd96e3210249c7af.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/8241a13ec6b6a7d6fd96e3210249c7af.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/8241a13ec6b6a7d6fd96e3210249c7af.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance through the map with Alice, and aim to reach various endings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/a92288ff28998f7e78681518ea275bdd.poster.avif?t=1751015236\" width=408 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/a92288ff28998f7e78681518ea275bdd.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/a92288ff28998f7e78681518ea275bdd.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Slay the Alice is a short visual-novel adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All you'll need to use is a mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Within a single map, you'll choose which path to take, read randomly-occurring stories, and choose Alice's actions.</p><p class=\