312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/66f7814c8220d0857a4f84dded22be63.webm?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048760/extras/66f7814c8220d0857a4f84dded22be63.mp4?t=1751015236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Game Streaming and Creative Guidelines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We welcome game streaming, live broadcasts, and fan creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > For game streaming, live broadcasts,  be sure to paste the URL for \"Slay the Alice\" on Steam in the summary field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Monetization is also allowed without any issues.</p>",
